column5: Great video Mike, yes I also liked number 3.  John
NIce.   Although, I am not too sure about a pike being in a Koi pond....

Wow. Very cool. I bet someone is emotionally scarred after #3.  I believe it. At the Toronto zoo they have a koi pond with a creek that flows through it. It had a fish gate but pike could easily squeeze through
That's insane... They musta been hungry. pretty brave fish... I wonder the fate of the cat lol
Neat videos. Hard to tell what's going on in #3. I was way back in my chair a little squeamish watching what was about to happen there.
Nature at it's finest,thanks for sharing Mike!
